{"altmetric_id":15843908,"counts":{"readers":{"mendeley":100,"citeulike":0,"connotea":0},"total":{"posts_count":19},"news":{"unique_users_count":6,"unique_users":["phys_org","nanometer_ru","moneyshow_stock_market","fat_pitch_financials_stock_quote","ein_newsdesk","asia_research_news"],"posts_count":6},"twitter":{"unique_users_count":10,"unique_users":["AnanikovLab","DMEremin","RealTimeChem","SNBakerLab","AzovVA","marseyt","630_5th_Ave","AnanikovLab_ru","ACSChemRev","khalilovlm"],"posts_count":11},"wikipedia":{"unique_users_count":1,"unique_users":["en:53076456"],"posts_count":1},"googleplus":{"unique_users_count":1,"unique_users":["Valentin Ananikov"],"posts_count":1}},"selected_quotes":["#Ions on #Friday! Future IOLIOMICS concept just defined in Chem.Rev. article @ACSPublications #Rea\u2026","IOLIOMICS A research discipline of the future @AnanikovLab","Our Chem.Rev. article after one month. Biological Activity .. and Application in Pharma and Medicine","Our Chem.Rev. article after one month. Biological Activity .. and Application in Pharma and Medicine @ACSChemRev","#Ions on #Friday! Future IOLIOMICS concept just defined in Chem.Rev."],"citation":{"abstract":"Ionic liquids are remarkable chemical compounds, which find applications in many areas of modern science. Because of their highly tunable nature and exceptional properties, ionic liquids have become essential players in the fields of synthesis and catalysis, extraction, electrochemistry, analytics, biotechnology, etc. Apart from physical and chemical features of ionic liquids, their high biological activity has been attracting significant attention from biochemists, ecologists, and medical scientists. This Review is dedicated to biological activities of ionic liquids, with a special emphasis on their potential employment in pharmaceutics and medicine. The accumulated data on the biological activity of ionic liquids, including their antimicrobial and cytotoxic properties, are discussed in view of possible applications in drug synthesis and drug delivery systems. Dedicated attention is given to a novel active pharmaceutical ingredient-ionic liquid (API-IL) concept, which suggests using traditional drugs in the form of ionic liquid species. The main aim of this Review is to attract a broad audience of chemical, biological, and medical scientists to study advantages of ionic liquid pharmaceutics. Overall, the discussed data highlight the importance of the research direction defined as \"Ioliomics\", studies of ions in liquids in modern chemistry, biology, and medicine.","altmetric_jid":"4f6fa4ea3cf058f6100024ed","authors":["Ksenia S. Egorova","Evgeniy G. Gordeev","Valentine P. Ananikov"],"doi":"10.1021\/acs.chemrev.6b00562","first_seen_on":"2017-01-27T01:42:47+00:00","funders":["niehs"],"issns":["0009-2665","1520-6890"],"journal":"Chemical Reviews","last_mentioned_on":1487784883,"links":["http:\/\/pubs.acs.org\/doi\/abs\/10.1021\/acs.chemrev.6b00562","http:\/\/dx.doi.org\/10.1021\/acs.chemrev.6b00562","https:\/\/www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov\/pubmed\/28125212","https:\/\/dx.doi.org\/10.1021\/acs.chemrev.6b00562"],"pmid":"28125212","pubdate":"2017-01-26T00:00:00+00:00","publisher":"American Chemical Society (ACS)","publisher_subjects":[{"name":"Chemical Sciences","scheme":"era"}],"scopus_subjects":["Chemistry","Physical Sciences"],"subjects":["chemistry"],"title":"Biological Activity of Ionic Liquids and Their Application in Pharmaceutics and Medicine","type":"article","mendeley_url":"http:\/\/www.mendeley.com\/research\/biological-activity-ionic-liquids-application-pharmaceutics-medicine"},"altmetric_score":{"score":55.05,"score_history":{"1y":55.05,"6m":0,"3m":0,"1m":0,"1w":0,"6d":0,"5d":0,"4d":0,"3d":0,"2d":0,"1d":0,"at":55.05},"context_for_score":{"all":{"total_number_of_other_articles":8445227,"mean":7.1001175639268,"rank":173267,"this_scored_higher_than_pct":97,"this_scored_higher_than":8271961,"rank_type":"exact","sample_size":8445227,"percentile":97},"similar_age_3m":{"total_n